WEBVTT	#Elemental Media Engine(TM) 2.17.0.0

00:00:00.00 --> 00:00:02.16
Actor Alec Baldwin was sued today

00:00:02.16 --> 00:00:04.74
by the family of the cinematographer he accidentally

00:00:04.74 --> 00:00:07.77
shot and killed on the set of his Western Rust.

00:00:07.77 --> 00:00:09.84
A lawyer for the family of Halyna Hutchins

00:00:09.84 --> 00:00:13.05
blames her death on, quote, "reckless conduct and cost

00:00:13.05 --> 00:00:15.75
cutting measures" by Baldwin and other producers.

00:00:15.75 --> 00:00:19.55
Baldwin claims he never pulled the trigger.